15

COUNTRIES. THE LARGEST SINGLE FOOTWEAR FACTORY ACCOUNTED FOR APPROXIMATELY

8%

OF TOTAL

FISCAL 2017

NIKE BRAND FOOTWEAR PRODUCTION. VIRTUALLY ALL OF OUR FOOTWEAR IS MANUFACTURED OUTSIDE OF THE UNITED STATES BY INDEPENDENT CONTRACT MANUFACTURERS WHO OFTEN OPERATE MULTIPLE FACTORIES. FOR

FISCAL 2017

, CONTRACT FACTORIES IN VIETNAM, CHINA AND INDONESIA MANUFACTURED APPROXIMATELY 46%, 27% AND 21% OF TOTAL NIKE BRAND FOOTWEAR, RESPECTIVELY. WE ALSO HAVE MANUFACTURING AGREEMENTS WITH INDEPENDENT CONTRACT MANUFACTURERS IN ARGENTINA, INDIA, BRAZIL, MEXICO AND ITALY TO MANUFACTURE FOOTWEAR FOR SALE PRIMARILY WITHIN THOSE COUNTRIES. FOR

