AND

2016

. THE COMPANY REGULARLY REVIEWS ITS AVAILABLE-FOR-SALE SECURITIES FOR OTHER-THAN-TEMPORARY IMPAIRMENT. FOR THE YEARS ENDED

MAY 31, 2017

AND

